23108918,https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/23108918,Small Auberge: Gaslamp Quarter/Convention Center#,"Welcome to Small Auberge This is the cutest and cozy loft in town. A perfect spot for a group of friends, coworkers or international travelers visiting the city.  Our place is only: -10 min away from the Airport(5-9$ Uber/Lyft) -10-15 Min walk to the Convention Center and the Gaslamp Quarter. -Close to the SD Padres stadium  -10 min drive to the beach and to Old Town(popularity attraction) -4 min drive to Balboa Park( North America Largest Urban Park) -6 min from the San Diego Famous Zoo","The loft is located in the Historic building of Isaac Lyon in East Village. The building has one of the most charming and outstanding features with a unique decor. 4 beds:  -1 bunk beds,  -1queen loft bed  - 1 Sofa  bed.  -1 Air mattress  - A well equipped kitchen Want to have an idea on how our place looks like? Please see the 3D video below:   (Website hidden by Airbnb)  Please see video below for instructions on how to park around our place:   (Website hidden by Airbnb)","Welcome to Small Auberge This is the cutest and cozy loft in town. A perfect spot for a group of friends, coworkers or international travelers visiting the city.  Our place is only: -10 min away from the Airport(5-9$ Uber/Lyft) -10-15 Min walk to the Convention Center and the Gaslamp Quarter. -Close to the SD Padres stadium  -10 min drive to the beach and to Old Town(popularity attraction) -4 min drive to Balboa Park( North America Largest Urban Park) -6 min from the San Diego Famous Zoo The loft is located in the Historic building of Isaac Lyon in East Village. The building has one of the most charming and outstanding features with a unique decor. 4 beds:  -1 bunk beds,  -1queen loft bed  - 1 Sofa  bed.  -1 Air mattress  - A well equipped kitchen Want to have an idea on how our place looks like? Please see the 3D video below:   (Website hidden by Airbnb)  Please see video below for instructions on how to park around our place:   (Website hidden by Airbnb)  Our goal is to give you a 5 ","The East Village is fast becoming San Diego's trendiest downtown neighborhood. This is where the locals go out. Coffee shops, Juice bars, restaurants, craft breweries and tasting rooms and great bars are all found here. Due to new development around the hostel, you may encounter some construction noises Monday-Friday 8am-5pm Also be aware that they are a lot of homeless people in the East Village and downtown San Diego in general. Nonetheless it is really safe to walk around(recommended that you walk with a friend at night time for female), wonderful and it is a lovely urban neighborhood.",We also host special events from birthday party to bachelorette/ bachelor weekend and comic week as well.  Please let us know when you book the loft for a Special occasion.,"You won't need to drive because our place is walking distance to everything. But in case you are looking for transportation, there are lot of options. Please see below: Trolley Station, only 2 blocks away from the loft Bike share, right in front of our building (You will need to download the app to rent a bike.)Please see our Guidebook when you check in. Less than 3 min wait for an Uber/Lyft","Our goal is to give you a 5 stars experience, and give you a memorable stay.",We will be available anytime to help you with any needs that may arise. We are here to welcome and take care of you when you visit our Small Auberge,- Quiet time starts at 10:30pm - please be respectful of the neighbors,,79310439,https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/79310439,Charline,6/22/2016,"San Diego, California, United States","Bonjour,

This is  Charline, and I am from the Ivory Coast. 
I have been living in sunny  San Diego for few years now, and I love everything about the city.

I work for a Commercial Real Estate firm, and I am also running my short-term rental business.

Dancing, cooking and traveling are my favorite things to do. My dream place to visit is Medellin, Colombia.

I enjoy being an Airbnb host, because I love meeting  people from different parts of the world.
My #1 priority as a host is to give my guests a 5 stars experience.

 I look forward to hosting you soon.",within an hour,100%,,f,University Heights,16.0,16.0,t,f,"San Diego, CA, United States",East Village,East Village,San Diego,CA,92101.0,San Diego,"San Diego, CA",US,United States,32.71037,-117.151,t,Loft,Entire home/apt,5,1.0,1.0,3.0,Real Bed,"{TV,Internet,Wifi,""Air conditioning"",Kitchen,""Paid parking off premises"",""Free street parking"",Heating,Washer,Dryer,""Smoke detector"",""Carbon monoxide detector"",""First aid kit"",""Fire extinguisher"",Essentials,Shampoo,""Lock on bedroom door"",Hangers,""Hair dryer"",Iron,""Laptop friendly workspace"",""Self check-in"",Keypad,""Private entrance"",""Hot water"",""Bed linens"",Microwave,""Coffee maker"",Refrigerator,Dishwasher,""Dishes and silverware"",""Cooking basics"",Oven,Stove,""Long term stays allowed"",""No stairs or steps to enter"",""No stairs or steps to enter"",""No stairs or steps to enter"",""No stairs or steps to enter""}",,$117.00 ,$117.00 ,$115.00 ,$75.00 ,3,$25.00 ,1,1125,57,114,2/17/2018,6/28/2019,Average,f,t,f,moderate,f,f
25298343,https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/25298343,"Retro Home 2 Bed/2bath Near Downtown, Zoo, Balboa","Welcome to our retro inspired home filled with natural light and vibrant color, offering TWO master suites with full private bathrooms. The space is fun and inviting and offers all of the comforts of home. If you like to cook we have a full kitchen, and great living area for relaxing. The neighborhood is our favorite, blocks away from food, cafes, local businesses, San Diego Zoo, Downtown, Gaslamp, Little Italy, Petco Park, The Convention Center and Balboa Park.",Our space is filled with color just like your hosts! We want you to have a fun and exciting experience while staying here. We simply love this neighborhood for it’s charm and how is located near the top sites of San Diego.,"Welcome to our retro inspired home filled with natural light and vibrant color, offering TWO master suites with full private bathrooms. The space is fun and inviting and offers all of the comforts of home. If you like to cook we have a full kitchen, and great living area for relaxing. The neighborhood is our favorite, blocks away from food, cafes, local businesses, San Diego Zoo, Downtown, Gaslamp, Little Italy, Petco Park, The Convention Center and Balboa Park. Our space is filled with color just like your hosts! We want you to have a fun and exciting experience while staying here. We simply love this neighborhood for it’s charm and how is located near the top sites of San Diego. Guests have full access to the unit and one parking space in the downstairs garage. You can reach out to us anytime and we will make sure to take care of any needs you may have. Our favorite part of this neighborhood is it's character and charm. Golden Hill is one of San Diego's most historic neighborhoods wi","Our favorite part of this neighborhood is it's character and charm. Golden Hill is one of San Diego's most historic neighborhoods with beautiful homes built in the 1800's. We are also a block away from the local shops, food places and cafes, which is super convenient. You can walk to everything you need. If you enjoy walking around the neighborhood we are at the southern end of Balboa Park.",We have wifi available and all the necessary items to make your stay comfortable and to ensure you have everything you need as if you were staying at your own home. There is no air conditioning and no TV.,"Feel free to get to the top spots in San Diego via bike, using the bike and scooter sharing apps (Lime Bike, Mo Bike, Bird, etc.). Your a quick bike ride to Downtown, Balboa Park, The San Diego Zoo and more. Walking is a great option as well as Uber and Lyft.",Guests have full access to the unit and one parking space in the downstairs garage.,You can reach out to us anytime and we will make sure to take care of any needs you may have.,- Quiet Hours: 10pm - 8am - NO Parties,,128459749,https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/128459749,Simone,5/1/2017,"San Diego, California, United States",,within an hour,100%,,f,North Clairemont,2.0,2.0,t,t,"San Diego, CA, United States",Golden Hill,Balboa Park,San Diego,CA,92102.0,San Diego,"San Diego, CA",US,United States,32.71514,-117.13807,t,Condominium,Entire home/apt,6,2.0,2.0,3.0,Real Bed,"{Wifi,""Air conditioning"",Kitchen,""Free parking on premises"",Elevator,""Free street parking"",Heating,""Family/kid friendly"",Washer,Dryer,""Smoke detector"",""Carbon monoxide detector"",Essentials,Shampoo,""Lock on bedroom door"",Hangers,""Hair dryer"",Iron,""Laptop friendly workspace"",""Self check-in"",Lockbox,""Private living room"",""Private entrance"",Bathtub,""Pack ’n Play/travel crib"",""Hot water"",""Bed linens"",""Extra pillows and blankets"",Microwave,""Coffee maker"",Refrigerator,""Dishes and silverware"",""Cooking basics"",Oven,Stove,""Single level home"",""Long term stays allowed"",""Well-lit path to entrance"",""No stairs or steps to enter"",""No stairs or steps to enter""}",,$137.00 ,$274.00 ,$200.00 ,$60.00 ,4,$20.00 ,2,30,89,178,5/30/2018,8/2/2019,Average,f,t,f,moderate,f,f
17975428,https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/17975428,"Spacious Condo w/ Balcony, Walk to Beach + Dining","Just a short walk to famous windansea beach, this well appointed three bedroom/two bath condo is located in the heart of La Jolla. Walk to a few nearby restaurants or just a short drive to many local restaurants and downtown La Jolla. Weekly and monthly discount pricing available, please inquire or check our website.","Located in the heart of La Jolla, within less than a 5-minute short walk to beautiful Windansea Beach and within walking distance to many local restaurants, this modern condo is also just a short 5-minute drive to trendy shopping, great dining experiences, and the unique vibes of famous La Jolla Village. This 3-story, 3-bedroom, 2.5 bath, 1620 sq. ft. tastefully decorated condo can be entered either through the garage or the front door of the main hallway.  The 2nd floor has a king master bedroom with a ceiling fan and an ensuite bath with dual vanities, and an oversized tiled walk-in shower.  There is also a 2nd queen guest bedroom here, also with a ceiling fan.  There is a hallway bath on this floor with a shower/tub combination which is shared by this queen bedroom and the 2nd queen bedroom on the 3rd floor. The 3rd level also features a well appointed, flowing great room with a spacious living room area with a large flat-screen TV, a ceiling fan to keep the air circulating, and lot","Just a short walk to famous windansea beach, this well appointed three bedroom/two bath condo is located in the heart of La Jolla. Walk to a few nearby restaurants or just a short drive to many local restaurants and downtown La Jolla. Weekly and monthly discount pricing available, please inquire or check our website. Located in the heart of La Jolla, within less than a 5-minute short walk to beautiful Windansea Beach and within walking distance to many local restaurants, this modern condo is also just a short 5-minute drive to trendy shopping, great dining experiences, and the unique vibes of famous La Jolla Village. This 3-story, 3-bedroom, 2.5 bath, 1620 sq. ft. tastefully decorated condo can be entered either through the garage or the front door of the main hallway.  The 2nd floor has a king master bedroom with a ceiling fan and an ensuite bath with dual vanities, and an oversized tiled walk-in shower.  There is also a 2nd queen guest bedroom here, also with a ceiling fan.  There is",,,,,,"While our #1 priority is insuring that our valued guests enjoy their stay with us, we also have an equally as important commitment to our neighbors and our community. Below are the house rules that we must enforce. Please read them prior to confirming your reservation. If you are not comfortable with these rules, we encourage you to please make alternate accommodations:  * Minimum age policy of 25 years of age  * Check-in is after 4PM | Check out is at 11am  * No smoking is allowed inside any of our properties or on the premises. * Overnight occupancy (including children and infants) is not to exceed the posted maximum occupancy. Occupancy is defined by the total number of people at the property at any time.  * NO PARTIES AT ANY TIME - a party is defined as any combination of the following; ANY loud noise and/or excessive drinking that is disruptive to neighboring houses and/or guests outnumbering the maximum amount permitted as defined above. A party will result in an immediate evicti",,122055416,https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/122055416,SeaBreeze,3/22/2017,"San Diego, California, United States","Since 2002, we have been providing an ever improving vacation home rental experience by exceeding guests expectations from start to finish. Our years of experience in the vacation rental industry ensures the highest level of customer satisfaction. We pride ourselves in setting an example as an honest, ethical industry leader with a high rate of return customers.",within an hour,99%,,f,Pacific Beach,403.0,403.0,t,f,"La Jolla, CA, United States",La 