19747289,https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/19747289,Centrally located Family Getaway in San Diego,"This Bay Park/Clairemont 3 bedroom house is situated on 1/2 acre with large pool (solar heated - cooler if cloudy), viewing deck, trampoline,  basketball net, BBQ and outdoor TV. Eat outdoors enjoying the garden view and the songbirds. Perfect for traveling families who want to see all that San Diego has to offer.  No A/C. 5 miles from popular Pacific Beach, Sea World and Old Town, 8 miles from the historic Gas Lamp Quarter downtown, 10 miles from the Zoo and 7 miles from La Jolla.",,"This Bay Park/Clairemont 3 bedroom house is situated on 1/2 acre with large pool (solar heated - cooler if cloudy), viewing deck, trampoline,  basketball net, BBQ and outdoor TV. Eat outdoors enjoying the garden view and the songbirds. Perfect for traveling families who want to see all that San Diego has to offer.  No A/C. 5 miles from popular Pacific Beach, Sea World and Old Town, 8 miles from the historic Gas Lamp Quarter downtown, 10 miles from the Zoo and 7 miles from La Jolla. Guests have the entire house.",,,,Guests have the entire house.,,- Quiet after 9pm - Rental agreement must be signed prior to check in.,,75282294,https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/75282294,Rich,6/1/2016,"San Diego, California, United States",,within an hour,100%,,f,Bay Park,1.0,1.0,t,t,"San Diego, CA, United States",Bay Park,Bay Park,San Diego,CA,92117.0,San Diego,"San Diego, CA",US,United States,32.79587,-117.19837,t,House,Entire home/apt,5,2.0,3.0,3.0,Real Bed,"{TV,Wifi,Pool,Kitchen,""Free parking on premises"",""Free street parking"",Heating,""Family/kid friendly"",Washer,Dryer,""Smoke detector"",""Fire extinguisher"",Essentials,Hangers,""Hair dryer"",Iron,""Private entrance"",""Hot water"",Microwave,Refrigerator,""Dishes and silverware"",""Cooking basics"",Oven,Stove,""Luggage dropoff allowed"",Other}",,$225.00 ,$675.00 ,$500.00 ,$150.00 ,1,$0.00 ,3,14,4,8,11/12/2017,6/29/2019,Very High,f,f,f,strict_14_with_grace_period,f,f
13814035,https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/13814035,Remodeled Apt. at top of Golden Hill,"My place is close to Turf Supper Club, Krakatoa, Luigi Pizzeria, and Starbucks Coffee. You’ll love my place because of it's well-lit, close to Petco Park, Comicon, and Gaslamp (5 min car ride or 30 min walk), a nice breeze comes through, 5 min walk to bars, liquor stores, and quick eats/coffee shops, the neighbors are really kind. .",,"My place is close to Turf Supper Club, Krakatoa, Luigi Pizzeria, and Starbucks Coffee. You’ll love my place because of it's well-lit, close to Petco Park, Comicon, and Gaslamp (5 min car ride or 30 min walk), a nice breeze comes through, 5 min walk to bars, liquor stores, and quick eats/coffee shops, the neighbors are really kind. .",,,,,,,,52345683,https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/52345683,Mehry,12/26/2015,"San Diego, California, United States",,,,,f,Golden Hill,1.0,1.0,t,t,"San Diego, CA, United States",Golden Hill,Balboa Park,San Diego,CA,92102.0,San Diego,"San Diego, CA",US,United States,32.71705,-117.14324,t,Apartment,Entire home/apt,3,1.0,1.0,1.0,Real Bed,"{TV,Wifi,Kitchen,""Free parking on premises"",""Family/kid friendly"",Washer,Dryer,""Smoke detector"",""Carbon monoxide detector"",Essentials,Shampoo,""Lock on bedroom door"",Hangers,""translation missing: en.hosting_amenity_50""}",,$186.00 ,$186.00 ,$175.00 ,$50.00 ,1,$0.00 ,1,5,3,6,7/24/2016,11/13/2016,Very High,f,f,f,flexible,f,f
22058710,https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/22058710,NEW Remodel 4 bd 3 ba Home Pool & Spa FREE Mid Stay Cleaning!,"Brand New Home, 4 bedroom 3 bath with Pool, Hot Tub, Cold A/C, large open concept Kitchen and Dining Rooms, Living Room with Large TV and new sectional sofa. Living room has sliding glass doors out to pool area! Master bedroom suite, guest bedrooms: Game Room with TV PlayStation sofa futon sleeper has a sliding door out to the pool, Queen Room and bunk bed room with 3rd bed sofa bed chair is a single sleeper child size. 2 hall bathrooms. Pool and hot tub and covered patio area with BBQ, & patio furniture! Walk into a bright and open Dining and Kitchen area, Living Room and Master bedroom suite is off to the right at the front of the house and the 2 hall baths and laundry closet are the first rooms as you'll go past from the kitchen toward the back of the house and other bedrooms: Game Room with sofa futon sleeper is the first room on the right, it has a sliding door out to the pool and patio area. 3rd bedroom has queen size bed, 4th bedroom: bunk beds and a sofa chair single bed child ","Accommodates: 9 Bathrooms: 3 Bedrooms: 4 Beds: 5 Property type: House Room type: Entire home/apt. Walk into a bright & open Dining & Kitchen area, Living Room & Master bedroom suite is off to the right at the front of the house & the 2 hall baths & laundry closet are the first rooms as you'll go past from the kitchen toward the back of the house & other bedrooms: Game Room with PS4 & games, sofa futon sleeper is the first room on the right, sliding door out to the pool & patio area. 3rd bedroom has queen size bed, 4th bedroom has  bunk beds & a sofa chair single bed child size mattress. Queen size Air mattress also available. All real beds have brand new organic mattresses! All appliances are brand new! Come be one of our first guests in this beautiful designer furnished & totally remodeled home!!","Brand New Home, 4 bedroom 3 bath with Pool, Hot Tub, Cold A/C, large open concept Kitchen and Dining Rooms, Living Room with Large TV and new sectional sofa. Living room has sliding glass doors out to pool area! Master bedroom suite, guest bedrooms: Game Room with TV PlayStation sofa futon sleeper has a sliding door out to the pool, Queen Room and bunk bed room with 3rd bed sofa bed chair is a single sleeper child size. 2 hall bathrooms. Pool and hot tub and covered patio area with BBQ, & patio furniture! Walk into a bright and open Dining and Kitchen area, Living Room and Master bedroom suite is off to the right at the front of the house and the 2 hall baths and laundry closet are the first rooms as you'll go past from the kitchen toward the back of the house and other bedrooms: Game Room with sofa futon sleeper is the first room on the right, it has a sliding door out to the pool and patio area. 3rd bedroom has queen size bed, 4th bedroom: bunk beds and a sofa chair single bed child ",North Clairemont,"Pool Temperature will be set by the management.  Spa can be controlled by guests. If you choose to heat the pool further, you will incur an additional $25 per day charge to cover the cost. An app is available for controlling spa temp & features from your phone, or provided Tablet. Please make a request beforehand if you would like to raise the temperature of the pool, as we will need to have the pool company adjust the chemical level for water safety. Gardener comes once a month on Tuesday. Pool cleaners come every Tuesday. Guests do not need to be home, the technician will come in through the side gate.  Trash day is Wednesday, guests are encouraged to take all bagged trash out to the large outdoor bins on the left side of the house on Tuesday afternoon in time for our maintenance man to roll the bins to the street Tuesday evening to be ready for early Wednesday morning pickup.",Bus stops are located just a few blocks away on the main street.,Guests have access to the entire 4 bedroom 3 bath main house & private backyard With pool & patio. Guests have driveway parking but no Garage access. Garage has been converted into a new Guesthouse which would be a great thing to rent together for larger groups if traveling with in laws or others who wanted privacy but also to be together on the same property. The studio will have its own private patio area & fenced gate in the driveway to access their unit. There is a locked gate separating the studios patio from the pool area which could be opened for groups who rent both the studio & main house. Studio guests will not have pool access otherwise. Nest smart thermostat keeps the home at a comfortable range.,"We are here for check-in check-out & anything you need in between. Our Goal is that all of our guests' experience is worth a 5 star review. If you are having a less than excellent experience, please contact us right away so we can remedy the problem!","Suitable for children (2-12 years) Suitable for infants (under 2 years) Pets allowed! No smoking. No parties or events. Additional rules Please also see the pool waiver, below the house rules While our #1 priority is insuring that our valued guests enjoy their stay with us, we also have an equally as important commitment to our neighbors & our community. Below are the house rules that we must enforce. Please read them prior to confirming your reservation. If you are not comfortable with these rules, we encourage you to please make alternate accommodations:    • Minimum age policy of 21 years of age unless accompanied by their parent / guardian.  (when using instant book; if under 25 please inquire)   • No smoking is allowed at any of our properties indoor or outdoor.   • Overnight occupancy (including children & infants) is not to exceed the posted maximum occupancy. Occupancy is defined by the total number of people at the property at any time.   **NO PARTIES AT ANY TIME – a party is ",,156086844,https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/156086844,Southern California Rentals,10/24/2017,"San Diego, California, United States","Southern California Rentals exists because we have a heart for hospitality. Much of our success has come from treating our guests like friends! We have welcomed people from all over the world and enjoy helping our guests find the best place to stay.  Our properties range in size from studios to 5 bedroom homes. Our priority is to help you feel at home throughout your stay! We are a family Business, my wife is a 5th generation San Diego Native, who has a lot of great tips and advice plus some fun family history that will make you feel like a local. I’m from Brazil and have an appreciation for anyone who travels from other countries, especially who speak English as a second language! That can be both challenging and rewarding and we are here to help you feel welcome, especially when traveling from far away. We know the best places to go, where to be and how to find whatever you need. Come stay in one of our properties and experience our beautiful home, San Diego!",within an hour,100%,,f,,16.0,16.0,t,f,"San Diego, CA, United States",North Clairemont,North Clairemont,San Diego,CA,92117.0,San Diego,"San Diego, CA",US,United States,32.83762,-117.17826,f,House,Entire home/apt,11,3.0,4.0,4.0,Real Bed,"{TV,""Cable TV"",Internet,Wifi,""Air conditioning"",Pool,Kitchen,""Free parking on premises"",""Pets allowed"",""Free street parking"",""Hot tub"",Heating,""Family/kid friendly"",Washer,Dryer,""Smoke detector"",""Carbon monoxide detector"",""First aid kit"",""Fire extinguisher"",Essentials,Shampoo,""24-hour check-in"",Hangers,""Hair dryer"",Iron,""Laptop friendly workspace"",""Private entrance"",""High chair"",""Babysitter recommendations"",Crib,""Pack ’n Play/travel crib"",""Game console"",""Full kitchen""}",,$289.00 ,$289.00 ,$695.00 ,$289.00 ,6,$50.00 ,1,365,16,32,8/31/2017,4/22/2019,High,f,t,f,strict_14_with_grace_period,f,f
18544040,https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/18544040,Cute Cottage walking distance to Beach and Village,"Light, airy 1 bedroom cottage attached to home with separate entrance.  Living room with kitchenette and dining area. Large bedroom with Cal King bed, bath with separated toilet/shower and sink/vanity area, walk-in closet. Bedroom has padded bench which can be made into additional twin bed if desired. Room for 3 people. 4 minute walk to beach, 1 minute walk restaurants and shops, kayak and surfboard rentals.","- Cable TV in bedroom - toilet/shower area separate from vanity/sink -  kitchenette w/microwave, toaster oven, full-sized refrigerator -  California King bed - Toaster, Coffee Maker. - Use of Iron, Iron board upon request - Shampoo, Body Wash - Towels - Use of Beach Chairs (2) and Umbrella upon request Perfect location 5 minute walk to the beach, and a comfortably furnished property. La Jolla Shores is a world-class beach for families with great swimming, snorkeling, kayaking and surfing. Kayaks, bikes and surfboard rentals are located just one minute away.","Light, airy 1 bedroom cottage attached to home with separate entrance.  Living room with kitchenette and dining area. Large bedroom with Cal King bed, bath with separated toilet/shower and sink/vanity area, walk-in closet. Bedroom has padded bench which can be made into additional twin bed if desired. Room for 3 people. 4 minute walk to beach, 1 minute walk restaurants and shops, kayak and surfboard rentals. - Cable TV in bedroom - toilet/shower area separate from vanity/sink -  kitchenette w/microwave, toaster oven, full-sized refrigerator -  California King bed - Toaster, Coffee Maker. - Use of Iron, Iron board upon request - Shampoo, Body Wash - Towels - Use of Beach Chairs (2) and Umbrella upon request Perfect location 5 minute walk to the beach, and a comfortably furnished property. La Jolla Shores is a world-class beach for families with great swimming, snorkeling, kayaking and surfing. Kayaks, bikes and surfboard rentals are located just one minute away. You have access to the e","We are located right in the heart of the Shores, only one minute away from the shops/restaurants and bars. Only a five minute drive into La Jolla Village, and located right down the hill from Scripps Institute of Oceanography and UCSD (this is a perfect space for visiting academics).",,"Off-street parking available upon request. The 30 bus stops directly outside the house, which takes you to on a short ride to UCSD/UTC or through La Jolla village, PB and to Old Town.","You have access to the entire self-contained apartment, with separate entrance from the main house.","I will greet you and show you around the apartment when you check in. You will have a separate entrance from the main house so you can maintain privacy, but if you need any assistance, I am always available to help.","- Quiet types only, no parties!",,3321906,https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/3321906,Maureen,8/20/2012,"San Diego, California, United States",From San Diego,within a few hours,100%,,t,La Jolla,1.0,1.0,t,t,"San Diego, CA, United States",La Jolla,La Jolla,San Diego,CA,92037.0,San Diego,"San Diego, CA",US,United States,32.85467,-117.25469,t,Bungalow,Entire home/apt,3,1.0,1.0,2.0,Real Bed,"{TV,""Cable TV"",Wifi,Kitchen,""Free street parking"",Heating,""Family/kid friendly"",Washer,Dryer,""Smoke detector"",""Carbon monoxide detector"",Essentials,Shampoo,""Lock on bedroom door"",Hangers,""Hair dryer"",Iron,""Laptop friendly workspace"",""Self check-in"",Keypad,""Private entrance"",""Pack ’n Play/travel crib"",""Hot water"",""Bed linens"",""Extra pillows and blankets"",Beachfront}",,$145.00 ,$290.00 ,$100.00 ,$65.00 ,1,$0.00 ,2,1125,116,232,7/17/2017,8/14/2019,Very High,f,f,f,moderate,f,f
27091191,https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/27091191,Your new SD home!,"I’m Stacy, 38!  Home w/ open living room/dining/kitchen area & washer/dryer. Room are furnished w/ beds & camping cot, couches (+price/person). Workout equipment in garage. Plenty of parking. Excellent location w/ access 52/5/805 & bus stops. 10 mins to beach, 15 to Downtown, 15 to Del Mar... Home is clean & you maintain personal items in common area. Interested in mature people who keeping home to a low rumble (no partiers!). We have jobs & classes which keep us busy!   Drug & smoke free!","The location is fantastic!  10 mins from the beach, 15 mins from downtown, 10 mins from La Jolla Shores, close to the freeways 52/5/805.  There is a shopping center 5 mins away with groceries, a movie theater, clothing, food, hardware store, dollar store and so much more!  Great central coastal location with easy access to all over San Diego!","I’m Stacy, 38!  Home w/ open living room/dining/kitchen area & washer/dryer. Room are furnished w/ beds & camping cot, couches (+price/person). Workout equipment in garage. Plenty of parking. Excellent location w/ access 52/5/805 & bus stops. 10 mins to beach, 15 to Downtown, 15 to Del Mar... Home is clean & you maintain personal items in common area. Interested in mature people who keeping home to a low rumble (no partiers!). We have jobs & classes which keep us busy!   Drug & smoke free! The location is fantastic!  10 mins from the beach, 15 mins from downtown, 10 mins from La Jolla Shores, close to the freeways 52/5/805.  There is a shopping center 5 mins away with groceries, a movie theater, clothing, food, hardware store, dollar store and so much more!  Great central coastal location with easy access to all over San Diego! As long as you put things back to original location you are more than welcome to use the kitchen, bathroom, laundry room, etc.  I ask that you wash and dry all ",,"House has skylights in the living room and bathroom as well as many windows  using natural daylight for an eco-friendly home.  We also recycle and compost !   This home host a smoke free environment so I ask that you only book if you don’t smoke anything at all.  People in this home are sensitive to smoke on clothing as well as luggage, etc so it would be best if you find a home that is not sensitive to it.  Thank you.",,"As long as you put things back to original location you are more than welcome to use the kitchen, bathroom, laundry room, etc.  I ask that you wash and dry all kitchen supplies.  Feel free to use the workout equipment in the garage!  I am in there 3 times a week with my trainer :)","Please ask any questions you may have!  I drive for Lyft so if you would like a ride I’d be more than happy to help you when I am free!!  I love meeting new people and having guests!  I have so many dear friends around the world whom I met through opening up my home to students, professionals, and travelers!  I am originally from Los Angeles and have lived in San Diego for 14 years.  Cheers! Because we have allergies in this home it is important that guests who book this home do not smoke in or outside the home.  Thank you.","You are welcome to use the kitchen as long as you respect the appliances and accessories by asking question, cleaning and putting dishes away after use. Please no smoking or drug use on or around property.  This is a quite home with professionals that have jobs so please be respectful of the space.",,77944255,https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/77944255,Stacy,6/15/2016,"San Diego, California, United States","Hello!
I’m a native So Cal kid.  I have lived in San Diego since 2004.  I’m originally from LA and would love to share my experiences with my guests.  I look forward to meeting travelers coming through San Diego and help out in any way I can!  I recently traveled thru a handful of countries in Southeast Asia and used AirBnb throughout the entire trip!  
Hopefully we will connect, cheers!!!",within an hour,100%,,t,,3.0,3.0,t,t,"San Diego, CA, United States",Bay Ho,Bay Ho,San Diego,CA,92117.0,San Diego,"San Diego, CA",US,United States,32.8303,-117.2214,f,House,Private room,3,1.0,1.0,1.0,Real Bed,"{TV,""Cable TV"",Wifi,Kitchen,Gym,""Free street parking"",Washer,Dryer,""Smoke detector"",""Carbon monoxide detector"",""Fire extinguisher"",Essentials,Hangers,""Hair dryer"",Iron,""Laptop friendly workspace"",Microwave,""Coffee maker"",Refrigerator,""Dishes and silverware"",""Cooking basics"",Oven,Stove,""Beach essentials"",""Luggage dropoff allowed"",""Long term stays allowed"",""Host greets you""}",,$60.00 ,$60.00 ,$200.00 ,$15.00 ,1,$30.00 ,1,1125,30,60,7/22/2018,7/28/2019,Very High,f,f,f,flexible,f,f
4190558,https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/4190558,Ocean View B&B Point Loma San Diego,"Ocean view bedroom with juliett balcony.  Private bath, access to the entire home, spa, pool & outdoor kitchen.  Breakfast included. Near airport, downtown Gas Lamp, Little Italy, SeaWorld, Balboa Park, Zoo, Old Town.  5 min. from ocean - Sunsets!","Ocean view & view of downtown in the Loma Portal area of Point Loma.  We often have a fresh ocean breeze blowing through our front door, even on the warmest of days.  Summer nights enjoy SeaWorld fireworks from our front deck.  In addition to your bedroom & private bath you will share our lovely home, built in the mid 40's & lovingly restored by my husband Jeff.  I think you will find this to be a very unique & inviting home.   We share our space with Toby, our dog & our cats Delilah & Cleopatra. In addition to your room & bathroom, you will have access to the living room, kitchen, front deck, back yard outdoor living space, including the outdoor kitchen, dining area, pool & spa. Continental breakfast is served daily ~ Vegetarian, vegan, gluten free & meat options are available. We are casual & laid back & hope you will be too.  We are here to help you in any way you might need & will honor your space & privacy ~ & at the same time will enjoy getting to know you! Point Loma is a lovely","Ocean view bedroom with juliett balcony.  Private bath, access to the entire home, spa, pool & outdoor kitchen.  Breakfast included. Near airport, downtown Gas Lamp, Little Italy, SeaWorld, Balboa Park, Zoo, Old Town.  5 min. from ocean - Sunsets! Ocean view & view of downtown in the Loma Portal area of Point Loma.  We often have a fresh ocean breeze blowing through our front door, even on the warmest of days.  Summer nights enjoy SeaWorld fireworks from our front deck.  In addition to your bedroom & private bath you will share our lovely home, built in the mid 40's & lovingly restored by my husband Jeff.  I think you will find this to be a very unique & inviting home.   We share our space with Toby, our dog & our cats Delilah & Cleopatra. In addition to your room & bathroom, you will have access to the living room, kitchen, front deck, back yard outdoor living space, including the outdoor kitchen, dining area, pool & spa. Continental breakfast is served daily ~ Vegetarian, vegan, glut","Close to Liberty Station - (URL HIDDEN) - with great restaurants, brewery, grocery stores & small clothing & art boutiques.  A 15 minute walk with a little bit of up & down hill action.  Just 5 minutes, by car from Ocean Beach with shopping & restaurants.",We are in the flight path.,"It is convenient to have your own car, but with Uber & Lyft, super easy.  We are  about a 10 minute walk down the hill where there is bus transportation which takes you to the Old Town Transit Center for further bus transport & trolly service.","You will have access to your own bathroom, living room, dining room, kitchen, front deck & the entire back yard with pool, spa & outdoor kitchen. Perfect for small gatherings, which we are happy to cater.","Jeff & I will be available, but not in your way.  We have created a package for you with some of our favorite restaurants & places to visit.  We would love to share some of our favorite spots with you.",The pool & spa are available till 11:00 pm.  No smoking or loud parties.,,9877759,https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/9877759,Carolyn,11/7/2013,"San Diego, California, United States","We are a conscious household & invite meditation or yoga by the pool or in our San Diego home.  
Although we are not vegetarian, we would be happy to prepare a vegetarian, vegan or gluten free breakfast for you.
I love to entertain, &  love being able to offer our homes to others.  I enjoy meeting people ~ my goal, is to create a peaceful, refreshing space for you.
In San Diego Point Loma, where we live, I will enjoy getting to know you & at the same time offer you plenty of privacy to enjoy the spectacular ocean views & sunsets & to relax in the back yard pool.  
At the magical Wildomar property, you will be on your own in with a private, spacious backyard, bar-b-que & fire pit ~ exploring the Santa Rosa Plateau & wine tasting in Temecula wine country, & maybe a day at Glen Ivy Spa.
Which ever home you choose, I feel certain you will want to return!",within an hour,100%,,t,Loma Portal,2.0,2.0,t,t,"San Diego, CA, United States",Loma Portal,Loma Portal,San Diego,CA,92106.0,San Diego,"San Diego, CA",US,United States,32.74521,-117.22397,t,House,Private room,2,1.0,1.0,1.0,Real Bed,"{TV,""Cable TV"",Internet,Wifi,""Air conditioning"",Pool,Kitchen,Breakfast,""Pets live on this property"",Dog(s),Cat(s),""Free street parking"",""Hot tub"",""Indoor fireplace"",Heating,""Suitable for events"",Washer,Dryer,""Smoke detector"",""First aid kit"",""Fire extinguisher"",Essentials,Shampoo,""Lock on bedroom door"",Hangers,""Hair dryer"",Iron,""Laptop friendly workspace"",""translation missing: en.hosting_amenity_49"",""translation missing: en.hosting_amenity_50"",""Children’s books and toys"",""Hot water"",""Host greets you""}",,$142.00 ,$284.00 ,$300.00 ,$50.00 ,1,$0.00 ,2,1125,52,104,1/19/2015,7/21/2019,Very High,f,t,f,moderate,f,f
19156481,https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/19156481,LIVE COMFORTABLY,This luxurious two-bedroom is located in beautiful Little Italy. Walking distance to everything this town has to offer and easy highway access to the 5 and 163. Every room is very clean and ready for guests to live comfortably.,"Please feel free to use everything this apartment has to offer. Also, take advantage of the grilling area and gym!","This luxurious two-bedroom is located in beautiful Little Italy. Walking distance to everything this town has to offer and easy highway access to the 5 and 163. Every room is very clean and ready for guests to live comfortably. Please feel free to use everything this apartment has to offer. Also, take advantage of the grilling area and gym! Everything We will leave key if we aren't home or meet you if we are! Walking!",,,Walking!,Everything,We will leave key if we aren't home or meet you if we are!,,,22626866,https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/22626866,Luke,10/16/2014,"San Diego, California, United States",,,,,f,Little Italy,1.0,1.0,t,t,"San Diego, CA, United States",Little Italy,Little Italy,San Diego,CA,92101.0,San Diego,"San Diego, CA",US,United States,32.72424,-117.16778,t,Apartment,Entire home/apt,4,2.0,2.0,2.0,Real Bed,"{TV,Wifi,""Air conditioning"",Kitchen,""Free parking on premises"",""Smoking allowed"",Gym,Elevator,Heating,""Family/kid friendly"",""Suitable for events"",Washer,Dryer,""Smoke detector"",""Carbon monoxide detector"",Essentials,Shampoo,""Lock on bedroom door"",Hangers,""Hair dryer"",Iron,""Laptop friendly workspace""}",,$200.00 ,$400.00 ,,,1,$0.00 ,2,1125,1,2,6/11/2017,6/11/2017,Average,f,t,f,flexible,f,f
21141356,https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/21141356,★Spacious Private& Comfy! Great for Large Groups!★,"Beyond spacious and well equipped, our 5000sqft property if perfect for large families, groups, weddings and more! Ongoing updates to this property keep it fresh and modern, inside and out!  The outdoors is as large as the inside, perfect for living the California lifestyle! Your guest will enjoy squeaky clean luxury bedrooms – all packed with amenities!  Situated between La Jolla shores and Pacific beach with easy access to all freeways. Only 15 min from downtown Gaslamp and convention areas.","Open floor plan, bright with 7 skylights and generously comfortable!  The common rooms flow into each other with comfortable seating areas throughout. The kitchen is the center of activities and from there you are part of all the goings on with plenty of room for Sous Chef’s! The outdoor area offers dining seating for 12, Fireplace seating and grilling areas, a generous yard and swimming pool all make for crowd pleasing fun! This home operates daily as San Diego Bed N Breakfast house, other than when the property is rented out to families or groups. That is why each bedroom has its own electronic lock, the dining area is spectacular, and the kitchen is so well stocked with cooking and serving ware – this is not your average vacation rental!!!","Beyond spacious and well equipped, our 5000sqft property if perfect for large families, groups, weddings and more! Ongoing updates to this property keep it fresh and modern, inside and out!  The outdoors is as large as the inside, perfect for living the California lifestyle! Your guest will enjoy squeaky clean luxury bedrooms – all packed with amenities!  Situated between La Jolla shores and Pacific beach with easy access to all freeways. Only 15 min from downtown Gaslamp and convention areas. Open floor plan, bright with 7 skylights and generously comfortable!  The common rooms flow into each other with comfortable seating areas throughout. The kitchen is the center of activities and from there you are part of all the goings on with plenty of room for Sous Chef’s! The outdoor area offers dining seating for 12, Fireplace seating and grilling areas, a generous yard and swimming pool all make for crowd pleasing fun! This home operates daily as San Diego Bed N Breakfast house, other than ",Working class neighborhood located between LaJolla shores and Pacific Beach. Easy access to the freeways and truly easy to get to all attractions from this family neighborhood!,We have Pond maintenance and yard maintenance which occurs weekly.,"Located on our brochure rack, you will find lots of fun activities along with bus schedules and how to get to San Diego attractions on public transportation. Uber and Lyft are great options! If you have never used them before, let us know and we will share a coupon code with you!",The entire home. Our Bed N Breakfast house office is locked off during your stay.,We are a vacation rental company - San Diego Resort Rentals and have a full team at your service!,"We are Pet friendly but do have a daily pet fee. There are cameras around the exterior of the property in public areas, not in the back yard. We have a fish pond in the back yard and renting the property means you are agreeing to feed the fish. We are on strict WSater / Energy restrictions.  We must as our guest to agree to the following: Use the dishwasher or washing machine before 2PM or after 9PK An Allowance of 8KWH per day of electric  is included in your rental.  A kilowatt-hour is 1,000 watts used for one hour. As an example, a 100-watt light bulb operating for ten hours would use one kilowatt-hour. The ladder is to be kept OUT of the pool when not in use and the pool cover is to be kept on. Gardner's come weekly to maintenance the back and front yard gardens. No more than 15 people are allowed on the property at any given time. Parties are not allowed unless express written arrangements have been made with the SDRR office.",,14823197,https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/14823197,Emily,4/28/2014,"San Diego, California, United States",,within an hour,100%,,f,Carondelet,17.0,17.0,t,t,"San Diego, CA, United States",Clairemont Mesa East,Clairemont Mesa,San Diego,CA,92117.0,San Diego,"San Diego, CA",US,United States,32.83347,-117.19045,t,House,Entire home/apt,14,3.0,4.0,7.0,Real Bed,"{TV,""Cable TV"",Internet,Wifi,""Air conditioning"",Pool,Kitchen,""Free parking on premises"",""Pets allowed"",""Free street parking"",""Indoor fireplace"",Heating,""Family/kid friendly"",""Suitable for events"",Washer,Dryer,""Smoke detector"",""Carbon monoxide detector"",""First aid kit"",""Safety card"",""Fire extinguisher"",Essentials,Shampoo,""Lock on bedroom door"",Hangers,""Hair dryer"",Iron,""Laptop friendly workspace"",""Self check-in"",Keypad,""Private entrance"",Bathtub,""High chair"",""Children’s books and toys"",""Babysitter recommendations"",""Pack ’n Play/travel crib"",""Children’s dinnerware"",""Hot water"",""Bed linens"",""Ethernet connection"",Microwave,""Coffee maker"",Refrigerator,Dishwasher,""Dishes and silverware"",""Cooking basics"",Oven,Stove,""Single level home"",""BBQ grill"",""Patio or balcony"",""Garden or backyard"",""Beach essentials"",""Long term stays allowed"",""Cleaning before checkout"",""Flat path to guest entrance"",""Well-lit path to entrance"",""Disabled parking spot"",""No stairs or steps to enter"",""No stairs or steps to enter"",""No stairs or steps to enter"",""Wide entryway"",""Handheld shower head"",""Fixed grab bars for shower""}",,$275.00 ,"$1,100.00 ",$500.00 ,$295.00 ,10,$20.00 ,4,90,19,38,12/28/2017,7/15/2019,Average,f,t,f,strict_14_with_grace_period,f,f
8685922,https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/8685922,"3BR2BA Townhome4, Steps to Beach, AC Garage Crib","This newly remodeled 1500 sq ft 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is 2 blocks to the sandy beach, 3 blocks to the heart of PB, and short drive to Seaworld, Balboa Park, Zoo.  It's equipped with CENTRAL A/C, baby gear, and beach gear. Primary guest must be 25",,"This newly remodeled 1500 sq ft 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is 2 blocks to the sandy beach, 3 blocks to the heart of PB, and short drive to Seaworld, Balboa Park, Zoo.  It's equipped with CENTRAL A/C, baby gear, and beach gear. Primary guest must be 25 Pacific Beach (PB) is popular for its prime location and is a great place to visit for a vacation all year round. Our beach is filled with surfers, sun bathers, swimmers, families and an endless supply of fun. The board walk is filled with roller bladders, runners and cyclists, or just the strollers and people watchers. It’s definitely a place where you can go and sit on a bench and enjoy all the different walks of life that Pacific Beach has to offer.  Crystal Pier, located in the heart of PB, and just a short 5 minute walk from our home is where you can find great beach shops, restaurants and cafes along the boardwalk. The beach continues south for about two miles becoming Mission Beach. At the south end of the beach area is Belmont Park wi","Pacific Beach (PB) is popular for its prime location and is a great place to visit for a vacation all year round. Our beach is filled with surfers, sun bathers, swimmers, families and an endless supply of fun. The board walk is filled with roller bladders, runners and cyclists, or just the strollers and people watchers. It’s definitely a place where you can go and sit on a bench and enjoy all the different walks of life that Pacific Beach has to offer.  Crystal Pier, located in the heart of PB, and just a short 5 minute walk from our home is where you can find great beach shops, restaurants and cafes along the boardwalk. The beach continues south for about two miles becoming Mission Beach. At the south end of the beach area is Belmont Park with the famous Big Dipper Roller Coaster at Belmont Park with fun rides, shops and restaurants. There is no shortage of “things to do” in PB, all within walking distance from our home. Garnet Ave and Mission Blvd are filled with places to eat, drink",,,,,,,45608374,https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/45608374,Stephanie,10/2/2015,"San Diego, California, United States","We are a family of four, boy age 10 and girl age 7.  We enjoy traveling and experiencing new places and activities.",within an hour,100%,,t,Pacific Beach,9.0,9.0,t,t,"San Diego, CA, United States",Pacific Beach,Pacific Beach,San Diego,CA,92109.0,San Diego,"San Diego, CA",US,United States,32.79366,-117.25048,t,Townhouse,Entire home/apt,8,2.0,3.0,5.0,Real Bed,"{TV,""Cable TV"",Internet,Wifi,""Air conditioning"",Kitchen,""Free parking on premises"",""Free street parking"",Heating,""Family/kid friendly"",Washer,Dryer,""Smoke detector"",""Carbon monoxide detector"",""Fire extinguisher"",Essentials,Shampoo,Hangers,""Hair dryer"",Iron,""Laptop friendly workspace"",""Self check-in"",Keypad,""Private entrance"",Bathtub,""High chair"",""Stair gates"",""Children’s books and toys"",Crib,""Pack ’n Play/travel crib"",""Children’s dinnerware"",""Hot water"",""Luggage dropoff allowed""}",,$250.00 ,$750.00 ,"$1,000.00 ",$150.00 ,1,$0.00 ,3,30,65,130,2/14/2016,7/6/2019,Very High,f,t,f,strict_14_with_grace_period,f,f
10001070,https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/10001070,Guest House Comfortable Upscale Area Cal King Bed,"Guest house with kitchenette, dining and sitting area, and a Sealy Posturepedic cal king bed (see reviews of how comfy)! The guesthouse has a smart tv, fast wifi, and self-check in. Our place is a fantastic getaway to wind down from your days adventure; conveniently located near SDSU in a safe, quiet family neighborhood. All San Diego attractions are only a short drive away.","Located in San Diego city limits, Del Cerro is an upscale safe family friendly area in close proximity North of SDSU. Our guests check in any time of the day with a combination deadbolt programed with a unique code specific to each guest.  The guest house is designed for self service; however, you can have as much or as little interaction with the host as you desire.  Free Wifi with convenient charging station. Sign into your netflix account on the large smart TV or check out what's on HBO/satellite TV (Directv).  The guest house was recently renovated top to bottom with new flooring, kitchenette, and shower.  It is stocked with coffee, tea, and all the equipment you need for light meals. It has a cal King bed that I would be happy to have as my own and a contemporary sitting area. Although City water is safe to drink, we take our water seriously. We have whole house water filtration, a water softener system, and provide a Brita filter pitcher for your stay. Linens are washed with a Sm","Guest house with kitchenette, dining and sitting area, and a Sealy Posturepedic cal king bed (see reviews of how comfy)! The guesthouse has a smart tv, fast wifi, and self-check in. Our place is a fantastic getaway to wind down from your days adventure; conveniently located near SDSU in a safe, quiet family neighborhood. All San Diego attractions are only a short drive away. Located in San Diego city limits, Del Cerro is an upscale safe family friendly area in close proximity North of SDSU. Our guests check in any time of the day with a combination deadbolt programed with a unique code specific to each guest.  The guest house is designed for self service; however, you can have as much or as little interaction with the host as you desire.  Free Wifi with convenient charging station. Sign into your netflix account on the large smart TV or check out what's on HBO/satellite TV (Directv).  The guest house was recently renovated top to bottom with new flooring, kitchenette, and shower.  It i","Del Cerro is a safe and desirable area of San Diego. It has great freeway access and is a short drive to all San Diego attractions.  It is very close to SDSU and Qualcomm Stadium. Mission Trails, Balboa Park, The SD Zoo, the Gaslamp District, and beaches are all a reasonably short drive away.","The guesthouse has a refrigerator/freezer, hot plate, toaster, and a microwave with a pizza oven; everything you need to prepare light meals.",A car is highly recommended. Public transit is available on Collage Ave about 1/4 mile away. The closest trolley stop is at SDSU. Uber and Lyft are prominent in the area as well.,"The guest house has Directv with HBO.  Free Wifi Smart TV - access to netflix, youtube","As often or as little as desired. There is private access to the guest house and some prefer to keep it that way. However, the host is always a call, text or a knock away. We are happy to provide San Diego insight, dining and entertainment ideas.",no additional guests / parties No smoking of any kind - including vapes No pets,,48142161,https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/48142161,Ann,11/4/2015,"San Diego, California, United States","I am a registered nurse responsible for surveying primary care clinics serving Medicaid members. I’ve been married for 30+ years and have two kids, empty nesters (primarily). We very much enjoy hosting, we’ve hosted guests from all over the world, so cool. ",within an hour,100%,,t,Del Cerro,1.0,1.0,t,t,"San Diego, CA, United States",Del Cerro,Del Cerro,San Diego,CA,92120.0,San Diego,"San Diego, CA",US,United States,32.78989,-117.07042,t,Guesthouse,Entire home/apt,2,1.0,0.0,1.0,Real Bed,"{TV,""Cable TV"",Internet,Wifi,""Air conditioning"",Kitchen,""Pets live on this property"",Dog(s),""Free street parking"",Heating,""Smoke detector"",""Carbon monoxide detector"",Essentials,Shampoo,""24-hour check-in"",Hangers,""Hair dryer"",Iron,""Laptop friendly workspace"",""translation missing: en.hosting_amenity_49"",""translation missing: en.hosting_amenity_50"",""Self check-in"",Keypad,""Private entrance"",""Hot water"",""Bed linens"",""Extra pillows and blankets"",Microwave,""Coffee maker"",Refrigerator,""Dishes and silverware"",Kitchenette,""Full kitchen""}",,$85.00 ,$170.00 ,$0.00 ,$60.00 ,1,$0.00 ,2,29,220,440,1/5/2016,8/10/2019,Very High,f,t,f,moderate,f,f
26741216,https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/26741216,Cozy Master room in Pacific Beach,"EXCELLENT LOCATION.JUST just 10 min to Downtown and 8 min to the beach in a quiet and safe neighborhood. We offer an spacious and sunny apartament MASTER ROOM with FULL bed and PRIVATE BATHROOM. Kitchen and dinning room shareable. We have 3 swimming pool in our complex and a jacuzzi, totally enjoyable for our guests! . No parties and pets allowed.  We would love to have you here :)",,"EXCELLENT LOCATION.JUST just 10 min to Downtown and 8 min to the beach in a quiet and safe neighborhood. We offer an spacious and sunny apartament MASTER ROOM with FULL bed and PRIVATE BATHROOM. Kitchen and dinning room shareable. We have 3 swimming pool in our complex and a jacuzzi, totally enjoyable for our guests! . No parties and pets allowed.  We would love to have you here :)",,,,,,- 10 pm- 8 am,,22028607,https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/22028607,Elena,10/1/2014,"San Diego, California, United States",,a few days or more,43%,,f,Bay Ho,1.0,1.0,t,t,"San Diego, CA, United States",Bay Ho,Bay Ho,San Diego,CA,92117.0,San Diego,"San Diego, CA",US,United States,32.80787,-117.21293,t,Condominium,Private room,2,1.0,1.0,1.0,Real Bed,"{TV,Wifi,""Air conditioning"",Pool,Kitchen,Gym,Breakfast,""Hot tub"",Heating,Washer,Dryer,""Smoke detector"",Essentials,Shampoo,Hangers,""Hair dryer""}",,$130.00 ,$130.00 ,$0.00 ,$40.00 ,1,$0.00 ,1,7,4,8,7/22/2018,7/6/2019,High,f,f,f,flexible,f,f
25078527,https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/25078527,Beach House between the Ocean and Bay,"Gorgeous 3-story, 3-bedroom, 2 ½- bath, 1 car + 1 compact car garage vacation home in Mission Beach. Nestled between the dynamic energy of the Pacific Ocean and the calm of Mission Bay, it’s the juxtaposition of two amazing worlds (just steps away from each other in opposite directions from the house).  An ideal getaway with the full gamut of beach pleasures. Immediate access to boating, surfing, biking, restaurants, shops, and more. Walk out the door and you’re steps from where you want to be.",,"Gorgeous 3-story, 3-bedroom, 2 ½- bath, 1 car + 1 compact car garage vacation home in Mission Beach. Nestled between the dynamic energy of the Pacific Ocean and the calm of Mission Bay, it’s the juxtaposition of two amazing worlds (just steps away from each other in opposite directions from the house).  An ideal getaway with the full gamut of beach pleasures. Immediate access to boating, surfing, biking, restaurants, shops, and more. Walk out the door and you’re steps from where you want to be.",,,,,,- Quiet hours- 10 p.m. Noise Ordinance- Please respect neighbors. It's a wonderful neighborhood. Families live here. Prefer guests over 30. Exceptions case by case.,,189579809,https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/189579809,Lee,5/14/2018,"San Diego, California, United States",My name is Lee. I live with my wife and daughter in San DIego. I love the beach and community and have great familiarity with places to go in the area. ,within a few hours,100%,,f,Mission Beach,1.0,1.0,t,f,"San Diego, CA, United States",Mission Beach,Mission Bay,San Diego,CA,92109.0,San Diego,"San Diego, CA",US,United States,32.78379,-117.25298,t,House,Entire home/apt,8,2.5,3.0,5.0,Real Bed,"{TV,Wifi,Kitchen,Heating,""Family/kid friendly"",Washer,Dryer,""Smoke detector"",""Carbon monoxide detector"",""Fire extinguisher"",Essentials,Shampoo,Hangers,""Hair dryer"",""Private entrance""}",,$300.00 ,$300.00 ,$250.00 ,$150.00 ,6,$