19858952,https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/19858952,Holland's House,"One bedroom apt, walking distance to downtown and Gaslamp district, convention center, Seaport Village, Little Italy, Balboa Park and the San Diego Zoo!! Brochure guide in apt for everything someone visiting could possibly want to do!! Visitor parking decal included during stay!",,"One bedroom apt, walking distance to downtown and Gaslamp district, convention center, Seaport Village, Little Italy, Balboa Park and the San Diego Zoo!! Brochure guide in apt for everything someone visiting could possibly want to do!! Visitor parking decal included during stay! I provide my phone number for guests to contact me about anything during their stay! My neighborhood is very quiet and family friendly! Close, if not walking distance to all the the amazing things San Diego has to offer! There are bus routes everywhere around here, also trolleys, coasters and trains! Uber and Lyft available to get around and very convenient!","My neighborhood is very quiet and family friendly! Close, if not walking distance to all the the amazing things San Diego has to offer!",,"There are bus routes everywhere around here, also trolleys, coasters and trains! Uber and Lyft available to get around and very convenient!",,I provide my phone number for guests to contact me about anything during their stay!,All I ask is that guests keep noise levels down between (URL HIDDEN) respectful of neighbors.,,57465724,https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/57465724,Holland,2/4/2016,"San Diego, California, United States",I'm a bartender and very laid back person. I'm always within a half mile when you're staying at my place and completely available to meet you if you need me for anything and will answer my phone for any questions or concerns you may have!,within a day,100%,,f,Cortez,1.0,1.0,t,f,"San Diego, CA, United States",Cortez,Cortez Hill,San Diego,CA,92101.0,San Diego,"San Diego, CA",US,United States,32.72228,-117.15734,t,Apartment,Entire home/apt,